N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 255.469 - External corrosion control: test stations

State Regulations

Each pipeline under cathodic protection required by this

Part must have sufficient test stations or other contact points for electrical
measurement to determine the adequacy of cathodic protection. Notes
